<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4658542>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGS. 24–31. Photomicrographs of Hartmannula angustipilosa from life (24, 25), after protargol (26) and silver nitrate impregnation (27–31). (24, 25) Dorsal (24) and ventral (25) views, arrows indicate contractile vacuoles. (26) Ventral view to indicate the kinetosome-like dots (arrow), macronucleus (double-arrowheads) and an ingested diatom (arrowhead). (27, 29) Ventral view of two specimens, arrows mark the contractile vacuole pores. (28, 30) Right-ventral view of two specimens,showing the position of contractilevacuole pores (arrows). (31) Silverline system on dorsal side. Bars: 20 µm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4658542/files/figure.png" .

